<body>
<div><head>《宋劉澂之永初山川記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.2">高祖即帝位於氾水之陽。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.3">黎陽有白馬塞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.4">孟達登之長歎。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.5">譙郡酇縣東忠有棘津亭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.6">故邑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-1a.7">呂尚所困處也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.2">介山即汾山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.3">子推逃隱於是山。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.4">陸渾縣有孤山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.5">西有伏流陂。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-2a.6">大石山在洛東北。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.2">新安有澗水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.3">源山北縣又有淵水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.4">未知其源。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.5">孝水出擅山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.6">擅山在宜陽縣西，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.7">在穀水南。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.8">洛陽城之西面有陽渠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-3a.9">周公制之也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.2">有水從沔陽縣南至梓潼、漢壽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.3">入大穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.4">暗通口山。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.5">《水經》濮水源出大騩山東北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.6">流注泗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.7">衛靈聞音於水上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-4a.8">殊為乖矣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a.2">蕭縣南有冒山。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a.3">白溝水。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a.4">安陂水旁有凌冢。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-5a.5">彭城西南有彌黎城。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.2">東莞縣箕山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.3">許由之所隱。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.4">陶朱冢在華容縣之西南。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.5">夏水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-6a.6">古文以為滄浪䱷水所歌也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.2">沅水自胡須枝分跨三十三渡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.3">逕交阯龍編縣東北入於海。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.4">黃水東北流，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.5">一涯谿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.6">通四會。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.7">贛縣東南有章水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.8">西有貢水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.9">縣治二水之間。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.10">二水合贛字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-7a.11">因以名縣焉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.2">三澨在竟陵縣界。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.3">並《水經注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.4">蒲坂城中有舜廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.5">城外有舜宅及二妃壇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.6">《史記正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.7">寧州鄣氣罔露，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.8">四時不絕。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.9">菵草名有毒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-8a.10">其上露觸之肉即潰瀾。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.2">肴有純石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.3">或謂石肴。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.4">北海有鄭元儒林講堂。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.5">永康縣縉雲堂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-9a.6">黃帝鍊丹處。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.2">彭城西南有項羽戲馬臺。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.3">魏武聽政殿前有聽政門。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.4">興平縣蔡子池南有石穴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.5">深二百許丈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.6">石青色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-10a.7">堪為硯。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.2">宜都郡有二大石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.3">一為陽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.4">一為陰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.5">鞭陰石則雨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.6">鞭陽石則晴。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.7">梓澤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.8">地名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-11a.9">去王城二十四里。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.2">費縣有積弩堂。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.3">廣陵縣東有梅池。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.4">建城縣西有羊山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.5">有然石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.6">色黃白而理疏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.7">以水灌之便熱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.8">可煮物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-12a.9">故謂之然石。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.2">艾縣有熱泉如湯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.3">以生物投之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.4">須臾爛熟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.5">並《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.6">大伾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.7">古黎國也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.8">《詩》云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.9">黎侯寓於衛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.10">以中露、泥中二句觀之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-13a.11">乃國名也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.2">宛陵北有敬亭山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.3">山有神祠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.4">即謝眺賽雨賦詩之所。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.5">其神云梓華府君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.6">頗有靈驗。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.7">昭山下有泉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.8">潭深無底，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.9">是湘水最深之處。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.10">昔有舟人沒於此潭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.11">其糟并甑有名題號，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.12">後於洞庭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-14a.13">尋得即知暗通也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.2">漢水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.3">古為滄浪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.4">即魚父所云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.5">滄浪之水清兮。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.6">今滄浪之水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.7">合流出鐔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.8">去北界山北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.9">蓋後人名之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-15a.10">非古滄浪也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a" ed="CHANT" n="001-16a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.2">安定處山谷之間，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.3">昆戎舊壤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.4">迫近夷狄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.5">修習武備，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.6">人皆以馳射為事。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.7">鼓山有石鼓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.8">形二所，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.9">南北相當，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-16a.10">二鼓相去十里。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a" ed="CHANT" n="001-17a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.2">九真都龍縣有雷廬羊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.3">大如犦牛。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.4">髯蛇吞鹿至角乃止。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.5">始興郡有大蛇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.6">名青蔥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.7">有大蛇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-17a.8">名赤頸。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a" ed="CHANT" n="001-18a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.2">石鄉有石室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.3">有仉生者居焉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.4">祝雞翁者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.5">洛陽人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.6">居尸鄉山下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.7">飬雞百餘年。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-18a.8">昌陽縣有昌水。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a" ed="CHANT" n="001-19a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.2">安邑有昆吾亭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.3">古昆吾國也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.4">臨安縣有石鏡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.5">在山之東峰。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.6">安帝義熙元年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.7">省射陽縣分廣陵之鹽城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.8">地立山陽東，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.9">城左鄉三縣為山陽郡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-19a.10">屬南徐山。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a" ed="CHANT" n="001-20a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.2">沔陽縣東有魯山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.3">山上有胡公祠。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.4">安陸居鄖城。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.5">吉陽縣西有九宗山。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.6">雲夢澤一名巴邱湖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.7">荊州之藪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.8">故魏武帝與吳主書云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.9">赤壁之困，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.10">過雲夢澤中有大霧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1680_CHANT_001-20a.11">遂便失道。<lb/></seg>
